{"ja488:0.1":"Jataka ","ja488:0.2":"Pakinnakanipata ","ja488:0.3":"Salikedaravagga ","ja488:0.4":"5. Bhisajataka ","ja488:1.1":"“Assam gavam rajatam jatarupam, ","ja488:1.2":"Bhariyanca so idha labhatam manapam; ","ja488:1.3":"Puttehi darehi samangi hotu, ","ja488:1.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi”. ","ja488:2.1":"“Malanca so kasikacandananca, ","ja488:2.2":"Dharetu puttassa bahu bhavantu; ","ja488:2.3":"Kamesu tibbam kurutam apekkham, ","ja488:2.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi”. ","ja488:3.1":"“Pahutadhanno kasima yasassi, ","ja488:3.2":"Putte gihi dhanima sabbakame; ","ja488:3.3":"Vayam apassam gharamavasatu, ","ja488:3.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:4.1":"So khattiyo hotu pasayhakari, ","ja488:4.2":"Rajabhiraja balava yasassi; ","ja488:4.3":"Sa caturantam mahimavasatu, ","ja488:4.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:5.1":"So brahmano hotu avitarago, ","ja488:5.2":"Muhuttanakkhattapathesu yutto; ","ja488:5.3":"Pujetu nam ratthapati yasassi, ","ja488:5.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:6.1":"Ajjhayakam sabbasamantavedam, ","ja488:6.2":"Tapassinam mannatu sabbaloko; ","ja488:6.3":"Pujentu nam janapada samecca, ","ja488:6.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:7.1":"Catussadam gamavaram samiddham, ","ja488:7.2":"Dinnanhi so bhunjatu vasavena; ","ja488:7.3":"Avitarago maranam upetu, ","ja488:7.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:8.1":"So gamani hotu sahayamajjhe, ","ja488:8.2":"Naccehi gitehi pamodamano; ","ja488:8.3":"So rajato byasana malattha kinci, ","ja488:8.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:9.1":"Yam ekaraja pathavim vijetva, ","ja488:9.2":"Itthisahassana thapetu aggam; ","ja488:9.3":"Simantininam pavara bhavatu, ","ja488:9.4":"Bhisani te brahmana ya ahasi. ","ja488:10.1":"Isinanhi sa sabbasamagatanam, ","ja488:10.2":"Bhunjeyya sadum avikampamana; ","ja488:10.3":"Caratu labhena vikatthamana, ","ja488:10.4":"Bhisani te brahmana ya ahasi. ","ja488:11.1":"Avasiko hotu mahavihare, ","ja488:11.2":"Navakammiko hotu gajangalayam; ","ja488:11.3":"Alokasandhim divasam karotu, ","ja488:11.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:12.1":"So bajjhatu pasasatehi chabbhi, ","ja488:12.2":"Ramma vana niyyatu rajadhanim; ","ja488:12.3":"Tuttehi so hannatu pacanehi, ","ja488:12.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi. ","ja488:13.1":"Alakkamali tipukannaviddho, ","ja488:13.2":"Latthihato sappamukham upetu; ","ja488:13.3":"Sakacchabandho visikham caratu, ","ja488:13.4":"Bhisani te brahmana yo ahasi”. ","ja488:14.1":"“Yo ve anatthamva natthanti caha, ","ja488:14.2":"Kameva so labhatam bhunjatanca; ","ja488:14.3":"Agaramajjhe maranam upetu, ","ja488:14.4":"Yo va bhonto sankati kancideva”. ","ja488:15.1":"“Yadesamana vicaranti loke, ","ja488:15.2":"Itthanca kantanca bahunametam; ","ja488:15.3":"Piyam manunnam cidha jivaloke, ","ja488:15.4":"Kasma isayo nappasamsanti kame”. ","ja488:16.1":"“Kamesu ve hannare bajjhare ca, ","ja488:16.2":"Kamesu dukkhanca bhayanca jatam; ","ja488:16.3":"Kamesu bhutadhipati pamatta, ","ja488:16.4":"Papani kammani karonti moha. ","ja488:17.1":"Te papadhamma pasavetva papam, ","ja488:17.2":"Kayassa bheda nirayam vajanti; ","ja488:17.3":"Adinavam kamagunesu disva, ","ja488:17.4":"Tasma isayo nappasamsanti kame”. ","ja488:18.1":"“Vimamsamano isino bhisani, ","ja488:18.2":"Tire gahetvana thale nidhesim; ","ja488:18.3":"Suddha apapa isayo vasanti, ","ja488:18.4":"Etani te brahmacari bhisani”. ","ja488:19.1":"“Na te nata no pana kilaneyya, ","ja488:19.2":"Na bandhava no pana te sahaya; ","ja488:19.3":"Kismim vupatthambha sahassanetta, ","ja488:19.4":"Isihi tvam kilasi devaraja”. ","ja488:20.1":"“Acariyo mesi pita ca mayham, ","ja488:20.2":"Esa patittha khalitassa brahme; ","ja488:20.3":"Ekaparadham khama bhuripanna, ","ja488:20.4":"Na pandita kodhabala bhavanti”. ","ja488:21.1":"“Suvasitam isinam ekarattam, ","ja488:21.2":"Yam vasavam bhutapatiddasama; ","ja488:21.3":"Sabbeva bhonto sumana bhavantu, ","ja488:21.4":"Yam brahmano paccupadi bhisani”. ","ja488:22.1":"“Ahanca sariputto ca, ","ja488:22.2":"moggallano ca kassapo; ","ja488:22.3":"Anuruddho punno anando, ","ja488:22.4":"tadasum satta bhataro. ","ja488:23.1":"Bhagini uppalavanna ca, ","ja488:23.2":"dasi khujjuttara tada; ","ja488:23.3":"Citto gahapati daso, ","ja488:23.4":"yakkho satagiro tada. ","ja488:24.1":"Palileyyo tada nago, ","ja488:24.2":"madhudo setthavanaro; ","ja488:24.3":"Kaludayi tada sakko, ","ja488:24.4":"evam dharetha jatakanti”. ","ja488:25.1":"Bhisajatakam pancamam. "}